text.tspan: Distribution of egalitarian democracy weighted by population, 2021
Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It combines information on voting rights, the freedom and
fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, as well as the extent to which the protection of rights,
access to power, and distribution of resources is equal. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Source: OWID based on V-Dem (v12), Gapminder (v6), HYDE (v3.2), UN (2019)
